        public static final LeanplumDeviceIdMode ADVERTISING_ID
        Uses the Android Advertising ID. Requires Google Play Services v4.0 or higher. If there is an error retrieving the Advertising ID, MD5_MAC_ADDRESS will be used instead.

        You also need the following line of code in your Android manifest within your <application> tag: 

        <meta-data android:name="com.google.android.gms.version" android:value="@integer/google_play_services_version" />
